features: Join the pore strip fan club! - With our Face Facts Forehead & Chin Strips, helps remove blackheads + unclog pores
Bizarrely satisfying to use - Leave these little strips on for 10-15 mins to bind to all the gunk on your skin and you'll know what we mean when you see what's left on the strip!
Lifts away dirt, excess oil and dead skin (Ahh) - While Witch Hazel is an amazing anti-inflammatory, helping to minimize the appearance of enlarged pores.
A great quick fix to remove unwanted build-up and blackheads - But you still need to be cleansing and exfoliating regularly to keep blackhead & excess oil at bay.
description: Product Description Bizarrely satisfying, these little strips bind to all the gunk on your skin and you'll know what we mean when you see what's left on the strip! Lifts away dirt, excess oil and dead skin (Ahh) while Witch Hazel is an amazing active, helping to minimize the appearance of enlarged pores. A great quick fix but you still need to be cleansing and exfoliating regularly to keep blackhead & excess oil at bay.
